    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cut the<strong> pork tenderloins</strong> into bite-sized pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Deseed the <strong>green</strong> and<strong> red pepper</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"><strong>[s]</strong></span> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and&nbsp;chop into bite-sized pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Peel the <strong>shallots</strong> and cut them in half</p>",
