    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid, with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>diced&nbsp;</strong><strong>pork <strong>tenderloin</strong></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>and cook for 1-2 min on each side&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Transfer the <strong>pork&nbsp;</strong>to a plate and return the pan to a medium heat&nbsp;</p>",
